<para style="p">A prayer of the afflicted when he is overwhelmed and pours out his lament before Yahweh.</para>

<para style="b" />

<para style="q1">

<verse number="1" style="v" />Hear my prayer, Yahweh;</para>

<para style="q1">hear my cry to you.</para>

<para style="q1">

<verse number="2" style="v" />Do not hide your face from me in my time of trouble.</para>

<para style="q1">Listen to me.</para>

<para style="q1">When I call out to you, answer me quickly.</para>
